   • ‘⚒’ - Current model supports tool calling
   • ‘≡N’ - Number of file attachments
   • ‘♁N’ - Number of web search results attached
   • ‘V’ - Reasoning/thinking sections hidden
   • ‘T’ - Token statistics display enabled

