18.4 Cloud Authentication
=========================

Authentication is handled via the Ollama CLI:

Sign In (‘M-x ollama-buddy-cloud-signin’)
     Opens your browser for Ollama cloud login.  Accessible from
     transient menu "Cloud Auth > Sign In".

Sign Out (‘M-x ollama-buddy-cloud-signout’)
     Signs out from cloud services.  Accessible from transient menu
     "Cloud Auth > Sign Out".

