     Verifies your authentication status.  Accessible from transient
     menu "Cloud Auth > Auth Status".

18.5 Automatic Manifest Pulling
===============================

Cloud models require a small manifest to be pulled locally before they
can be used.  Ollama Buddy handles this automatically: when you select a
cloud model for the first time, the manifest is fetched via ‘ollama
pull’ before your prompt is sent.  You will see a brief "Pulling cloud
model manifest..."  message during this process.

